item.title: A Title with Enthusiasm! Not This One, the Main Blog Title
item.description: I actually took the time to come up with something creative and enticing as my blog title. I adapted (okay, maybe just straight out stole) the 2019 theme of the Tor Project. Plus, behing the seen, I modified the information in my meta tag to help with SEO. Oh yeah, I added a publishing footer for each blog post.
item.author: nicoleiocana@gmail.com (Nicolei Ocana)
